These colonists have serious ash buildup:

{0}

Ash buildup is usually caused by being outside, or in a caravan, during an ash storm. Buildup will reduce while under a roof, or once the storm has ended. Caravans will be protected against ash buildup while resting, allowing members to recover from buildup.
